channel.title: Object Spawning
channel.description:

1. Is there a certain amount of objects you can spawn? 2. Is there another way to spawn objects? 3. Are there certain places you can't spawn things? (i was trying in wildy by choas elements)
Thanks ~Legit Gltich~
